snippet.title: De Grisogono Red Carpet ft Cara Delevingne, Amber Heard at Eden Roc, Cannes 2014 | FashionTV
snippet.description:
http://www.FashionTV.com/videos CANNES - Join FashionTV on the red carpet in Cannes! Celebs flow down the red carpet as they arrive to the De Grisogono party at Eden Roc in Cannes during the 2014 Cannes Film Festival.

Appearances: Sharon Stone, Antonio Banderas, Fawaz Gruosi De Grisogono CEO, Cara Delevingne, Paris Hilton, Ana Beatriz Barros, Amber Heard
